      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay thats a relief. i was getting kind of worried. i also noticed i've been feeling a bit dizzy and my head feels kind of fuzzy sometimes too. i read somewhere online that you should drink a ton of water to help flush it out if you feel these things, do you think i should just double my water intake today to help with the nausea and shaking?",
